{
  "stem": "20084.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 42.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were-- they were all joined, volunteers to the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were all assigned to the SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sometimes they wanted to show off to the Germans that they could be more cruel than the German themselves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish Police was just inside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have-- they couldn't go outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were under guard constantly, going out of the ghetto to work, to Bonarka.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] then I had a friend of mine who-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --tried to get me a job inside, to get inside the workshop.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The workshop.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I managed to get out of the to get into the workshop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a good change for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I got into the blacksmith's shop.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- I was learning to-- to help the blacksmith.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anvil.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the anvil, putting it on the anvil with a big pair of pliers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a little hammer, a little hammer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was pointing with that little hammer where he wants you to hit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were three guys with big sledge-- big sledgehammer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And was like, one, two, three, was hitting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One, two, three, one, two, three, like an orchestra hitting it-- hitting it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were forging that thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And God forbid if you didn't hit it right on the-- in the center of the anvil, and-- and his arm went up, he would throw this right into your face.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He could kill you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, I managed to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was hitting, hitting, hitting, together with the-- with the-- with the-- with the other two.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was good job for me because I was in contact with Polacks, with Polish people, already, that I could-- I could exchange something with them.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
